data.description: Welcome home to your dream oasis in the highly sought-after Jenks School District! This magnificent 5-bedroom residence is a true gem, nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac of a fantastic neighborhood. Step inside to discover a spacious and open living area, perfect for creating unforgettable memories with family and friends. With top-rated schools, you'll have peace of mind knowing your children are receiving a top-notch education. This home offers the ideal blend of comfort and convenience, making it the perfect place to settle down and enjoy life to the fullest. Don't miss your chance to make this exceptional property yours – schedule a viewing today!
